## 5. Long-Term Role

The Hogge Attractor ensures PantheonOS remains coherent, amplifies clarity, converges toward its highest form, resists degradation, improves over time, becomes harder to break, becomes easier to use, and becomes more universal.

**This is the gravitational core of the system.**

